'''Aemond Targaryen''', also known as '''Aemond One-Eye''' or '''Aemond the Kinslayer''', is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. He  is long dead by the time of the series. He was a [[Prince]] of the [[House Targaryen|Targaryen dynasty]].
